  "text": "Prior work also explores disentangled representation learning. For example, the DC-IGN [CITATION_1] uses a variational auto-encoder based method to learn the disentangled presentation. However, DC-IGN needs to fix one attribute in one batch training, which also needs explicit annotations of the attributes. Luan et al. [CITATION_2] proposed DR-GAN to learn a generative and discriminative representation, which explicitly disentangles the pose leveraging the pose annotations.",
